installation.script:
#!/bin/bash


#download server files
echo "running: curl -sSL -o https://s3.amazonaws.com/ut2004-files/dedicated-server-3339-bonuspack.tar.gz"
curl -sSL -o dedicated-server-3339-bonuspack.tar.gz https://s3.amazonaws.com/ut2004-files/dedicated-server-3339-bonuspack.tar.gz

#unpack
mkdir -p /mnt/server
tar -xzvf dedicated-server-3339-bonuspack.tar.gz --strip-components=1 -C /mnt/server/
cp -R /mnt/server/ut-server/* /mnt/server
rm -rf /mnt/server/ut-server
rm -rf mnt/server/System/UT2004.ini

#get setup files
echo "Downloading setup files"
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GFXSpeed/ut2004_pterodactyl/main/setup_files/UT2004.ini>> mnt/server/System/UT2004.ini
curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/trentnbauer/PelicanEggs/blob/main/ut2004/start.sh>> mnt/server/start.sh\

echo "Generating cdkey file"
touch /mnt/server/System/cdkey

#set permissions
echo "Fixing permissions"
find /mnt/server/ -type d -exec chmod 755 {} +
find /mnt/server/ -type f -exec chmod 644 {} +
chmod +x /mnt/server/System/ucc-bin
chmod +x /mnt/server/start.sh

cd /mnt/server || exit

chown -R root:root /mnt

export HOME=/mnt/server

## install end
echo "-----------------------------------------"
echo "Installation completed..."
echo "-----------------------------------------"
